PrecisAmendments to the CHILD CARE EXPENSE AND MOVING EXPENSE REMISSION ORDER which extend the cut-off date for making an application from December 31, 1991 to December 31, 1995, in those cases where an objection or court appeal was outstanding on December 31, 1991, including cases before the Federal Court.

precis:
Amendments to the CHILD CARE EXPENSE AND MOVING EXPENSE REMISSION ORDER
which extend the cut-off date for making an application from December 31,
1991 to December 31, 1995, in those cases where an objection or court
appeal was outstanding on December 31, 1991, including cases before the
Federal Court.
